{"tid":2058332,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拆解華為旗艦平板   美國零件只佔 2% 日本超過 8 成","createTime":"2020-06-10T05:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T08:17:19.000Z","uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc31f6e71c2d264cad84ed88a653a0d4410bfb3","tid":2058332,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:36:33.000Z","msg":"華為一直是大陸手機生產商的龍頭，其產品所使用的零件來源一直備受關注，尤其是集團被納入美國的實體名單，無法採購和使用美國零件和技術之後。近日有大陸網站拆解旗艦級 Android 平板，發現 1,411 件零件中只有 28 件來自美國。<br />\n<br />\n華為 MatePad Pro 的零件主要來自中國大陸和日本，另外還有德國、荷蘭、奧地利和韓國等供應商。日本零件達 1,148 件，佔整體 81.4%，而中國零件有 225 件，佔整體 15.9%，美國的 28 件零件佔整體 2%，至於韓國的零件則只有 3 件，佔 0.2%。雖然日本零件數量最多，但實際佔平板的物料成本 4.6%，中國的零件數量排第二，物料成本卻佔 71%。<br />\n<br />\n韓國零件雖然只得 3 件，但佔物料成本的 15.7%，而美國零件的物料成本約為 4.6%。大陸傳媒指為了應對美國的禁令，華為除了在禁令生效前囤積零件，亦開始尋找韓國的設備以取代美國的設備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/06/09/huawei-matepad-pro-parts-origin/notebook/tablet-notebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F06%2F09%2Fhuawei-matepad-pro-parts-origin%2Fnotebook%2Ftablet-notebook%2F&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVax5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=1526ec0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/06/09/huawei-matepad-pro-parts-origin/notebook/tablet-notebook/</a>"},{"pid":"33149638d705379441b880623f22955a3568cec9","tid":2058332,"uid":343361,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"美國技術占100%<br />\n完"},{"pid":"a62a2b65fd0fa3403113f4fe01ef26850c12e966","tid":2058332,"uid":230511,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:39:44.000Z","msg":"美國零件只佔2%<br />\n但呢2%決定部機係21世紀水平定係20世紀水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95f8bcb478595113b455be1ae048c67d506a987","tid":2058332,"uid":61280,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:49:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"f